{"tid":2021412,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「屎家軍」係藍又點？","createTime":"2020-05-17T17:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T16:12:43.000Z","uid":333451,"like":28,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d98f1b9f1cd1abe0aa0f3330f82bdc8cb2c44db1","tid":2021412,"uid":333451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T17:05:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">首先利申我認同杯葛CGA、屎萊姆等人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但如果參加個圍爐Christmas party又係「屎家軍」<br />\n一齊拍過片又係 咁我地會傷及無辜<br />\n<br />\n隨便舉例 Auman黃到比人拉 Auman屬於攪屎棍<br />\n攪屎棍同屎軍又熟 幫佢地搞過party <br />\n咁我杯唔杯葛好？個乜撚eg又好熟佢地<br />\n<br />\n其實如果政府、CGA細b、屎個關係咁明顯<br />\n杯葛屎係必行咁上下<br />\n不過亦只係做到呢步就夠<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">學大家講 冷處理啦</span><br />\n<br />\n個人認為 youtuber點都知得多過我地 真黃發現藍絲會自動割 我地唔需要浪費時間<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">再個人認為 梁君彥委任、國歌法、監警會更迫切 亦係我地非youtube圈內人應該留意同應對</span>"},{"pid":"10db22b6c87be4141b35c0819b6177741bec3429","tid":2021412,"uid":333451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T17:07:19.000Z","msg":"推唔郁 認同就幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港"},{"pid":"28912dbb289791f15ab9a3bf9542b24b45b15965","tid":2021412,"uid":49018,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T17:19:02.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n熱門成堆屎唔知做乜"},{"pid":"142b03915a37215c4e361a8b847f1c96c3a1648e","tid":2021412,"uid":333451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28912dbb289791f15ab9a3bf9542b24b45b15965","tid":2021412,"uid":49018,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T17:19:02.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n熱門成堆屎唔知做乜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T17:21:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"464d916e34a939f98dba00d43eea9d2409ff25aa","tid":2021412,"uid":78300,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"28912dbb289791f15ab9a3bf9542b24b45b15965","tid":2021412,"uid":49018,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"c